n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseScrollEvent\"><code>MouseScrollEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MSManipulationEvent\"><code>MSManipulationEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PictureInPictureEvent\"><code>PictureInPictureEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TaskPriorityChangeEvent\"><code>TaskPriorityChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Touch_events\"><code>Touch_events</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRReferenceSpaceEvent\"><code>XRReferenceSpaceEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSessionEvent\"><code>XRSessionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Canvas API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/createImageBitmap\"><code>createImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong><code>RenderingContext</code></strong> ist eine WebIDL-<code>typedef</code>, die auf eine beliebige der Schnittstellen verweisen kann, die einen Grafik-Rendering-Kontext innerhalb eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> Elements darstellen: <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext</code></a> oder <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL2RenderingContext\"><code>WebGL2RenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</span></p>\n\n<p>Durch die Verwendung der Kurzform <code>RenderingContext</code> können Methoden und Eigenschaften, die eine beliebige dieser Schnittstellen verwenden können, einfacher spezifiziert und geschrieben werden; da <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> mehrere Rendering-Systeme unterstützt, ist es aus Sicht der Spezifikation und der Browser-Implementierung hilfreich, eine Kurzform zu verwenden, die \"eine dieser Schnittstellen\" bedeutet.</p>\n\n<p>Als solches ist <code>RenderingContext</code> ein Implementierungsdetail und nicht etwas, das Webentwickler direkt verwenden. Es gibt keine <code>RenderingContext</code>-Schnittstelle, und es gibt keine Objekte, die den Typ <code>RenderingContext</code> implementieren.</p>\n\n<p>Die primäre Verwendung dieses Typs ist die Definition der <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/getContext\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Methode des <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code>-Elements, die einen <code>RenderingContext</code> (d.h. einen beliebigen der Rendering-Kontext Typen) zurückgibt.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"<span class=\"tlid-translation translation\" lang=\"de\"><span title=\"\">Spezifikationen</span></span>","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\"><span class=\"tlid-translation translation\" lang=\"de\"><span title=\"\">Spezifikationen</span></span></th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#renderingcontext\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'RenderingContext' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Erstdefinition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>","titleAsText":"Spezifikationen"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Die Rendering-Kontext-Schnittstellen:<br>\n  <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext</code></a>, und <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL2RenderingContext\"><code>WebGL2RenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Guide/Graphics\">Grafiken im Internet</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a> und <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API\">WebGL</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"<span class=\"tlid-translation translation\" lang=\"de\"><span title=\"\">Spezifikationen</span></span>","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"RenderingContext ist eine WebIDL-typedef, die auf eine beliebige der Schnittstellen verweisen kann, die einen Grafik-Rendering-Kontext innerhalb eines <canvas> Elements darstellen: CanvasRenderingContext2D, WebGLRenderingContext oder WebGL2RenderingContext (en-US).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"RenderingContext","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"de/orphaned/web/api/renderingcontext","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/orphaned/web/api/renderingcontext/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"RenderingContext | MDN","noIndexing":true}}